1
00:01:05,856 --> 00:01:08,288
=No Doubt In Us=
(Adapted from the Manman comic No Doubt in Us)

2
00:01:08,416 --> 00:01:11,328
=Episode 4=

3
00:01:12,360 --> 00:01:14,720
Xiao Jinyun has been
acting strangely lately.

4
00:01:14,720 --> 00:01:16,561
So as the Empress.

5
00:01:17,720 --> 00:01:19,880
Haven't you found this suspicious?

6
00:01:20,600 --> 00:01:23,160
Xu Yu is simple-minded and not a threat.

7
00:01:23,360 --> 00:01:24,880
As for Xiao Jinyun,

8
00:01:25,561 --> 00:01:27,281
isn't your father investigating him?

9
00:01:27,281 --> 00:01:28,880
Focusing solely on Xiao Jinyun

10
00:01:29,041 --> 00:01:30,561
will only make you blind.

11
00:01:30,960 --> 00:01:34,001
Xiao Jinyun matters most, not Xu Yu.

12
00:01:35,641 --> 00:01:37,240
You don't understand her.

13
00:01:38,201 --> 00:01:40,320
The messenger from the north
will arrive shortly.

14
00:01:41,121 --> 00:01:43,001
It's best to ensure nothing goes wrong.

15
00:01:43,761 --> 00:01:47,001
Then leave the task
of testing Xu Yu to me.

16
00:01:47,360 --> 00:01:49,401
No matter how you test her,

17
00:01:49,401 --> 00:01:51,201
please ensure she gets no harm.

18
00:01:51,440 --> 00:01:53,160
The Empress

19
00:01:53,720 --> 00:01:55,240
is of great use to us.

20
00:01:57,356 --> 00:01:59,392
(Xiao Jinle)

21
00:02:44,081 --> 00:02:46,440
No, this scent is completely wrong!

22
00:02:46,497 --> 00:02:47,081
Get lost!

23
00:03:02,977 --> 00:03:06,294
(Five years ago)

24
00:03:08,961 --> 00:03:09,841
Sorry.

25
00:03:10,440 --> 00:03:12,401
I just enjoy meddling in others' affairs

26
00:03:12,401 --> 00:03:13,920
and despise people like you,

27
00:03:13,920 --> 00:03:16,440
who could fight back
but just silently take a beating.

28
00:03:17,081 --> 00:03:19,600
Whether you're courting death
or you just seek for punishment,

29
00:03:19,880 --> 00:03:22,121
since I know it, I won't stand by.

30
00:03:31,320 --> 00:03:31,880
Take it.

31
00:03:36,281 --> 00:03:37,640
Not any good news?

32
00:03:37,920 --> 00:03:39,320
Why come to report then?

33
00:03:40,001 --> 00:03:41,081
Please calm your anger.

34
00:03:41,480 --> 00:03:43,600
She was merely reporting

35
00:03:43,600 --> 00:03:44,720
what she saw yesterday.

36
00:03:45,401 --> 00:03:48,640
What matters now is His Majesty
staying in Fengyi Palace every night.

37
00:03:48,801 --> 00:03:51,720
Even the Empress Dowager has become
much more lenient towards the Empress.

38
00:03:52,320 --> 00:03:53,440
No wonder

39
00:03:53,801 --> 00:03:55,561
Xu Yu gave me the Empress's Seal.

40
00:03:58,440 --> 00:04:00,961
She wanted to use palace affairs

41
00:04:00,961 --> 00:04:02,160
to tie me down,

42
00:04:02,320 --> 00:04:03,841
allowing her to keep His Majesty!

43
00:04:05,480 --> 00:04:07,160
Why couldn't you keep His Majesty?

44
00:04:10,801 --> 00:04:13,880
You're the only one in the entire palace
carrying the imperial heir,

45
00:04:14,961 --> 00:04:16,601
yet His Majesty doesn't go to see you?

46
00:04:17,840 --> 00:04:20,361
His Majesty was never close to me.

47
00:04:21,041 --> 00:04:21,721
Useless!

48
00:04:24,921 --> 00:04:25,481
Consort,

49
00:04:26,080 --> 00:04:28,200
if you wish to separate
His Majesty and the Empress,

50
00:04:29,041 --> 00:04:30,320
I do have a plan.

51
00:04:33,440 --> 00:04:36,200
General Chen resolved the grain
issue just like that?

52
00:04:37,361 --> 00:04:41,400
General Chen and Chancellor Zhao
has been at odds in court,

53
00:04:41,721 --> 00:04:43,161
but when it comes to wars,

54
00:04:43,161 --> 00:04:44,681
they will do everything possible

55
00:04:44,681 --> 00:04:46,880
to make the Ministry of Revenue
comply anyway.

56
00:04:48,481 --> 00:04:51,041
Although that day you did not act
according to my instructions,

57
00:04:51,361 --> 00:04:52,121
however,

58
00:04:52,721 --> 00:04:53,960
you established my authority.

59
00:04:54,440 --> 00:04:56,001
(Should I tell him about what I heard)

60
00:04:56,097 --> 00:04:57,481
(in the Xunfang Pavilion?)

61
00:04:58,080 --> 00:04:59,601
(Will he believe the Xu family?)

62
00:05:01,481 --> 00:05:02,440
One more matter.

63
00:05:02,640 --> 00:05:04,760
Greetings, Your Majesties.

64
00:05:07,080 --> 00:05:09,001
Lady Tao, you are pregnant.
No need to bow.

65
00:05:13,001 --> 00:05:14,001
Your Majesty,

66
00:05:14,280 --> 00:05:15,760
why did you push me?

67
00:05:16,481 --> 00:05:17,760
When did I ever push you?

68
00:05:18,840 --> 00:05:19,481
Your Majesty.

69
00:05:19,880 --> 00:05:20,400
Your Majesty.

70
00:05:20,561 --> 00:05:22,440
My stomach hurts so much.

71
00:05:22,721 --> 00:05:23,361
It hurts!

72
00:05:24,001 --> 00:05:24,640
Your Majesty.

73
00:05:24,921 --> 00:05:25,760
I did not push her.

74
00:05:26,625 --> 00:05:28,361
Guards, summon the imperial physician!

75
00:05:29,400 --> 00:05:30,320
Your Majesty!

76
00:06:00,960 --> 00:06:03,880
Imperial Physician Feng.
How are Lady Tao and the unborn child?

77
00:06:04,320 --> 00:06:05,161
Your Majesty,

78
00:06:05,161 --> 00:06:06,960
Lady Tao's pulse is deep,
faint, and thready,

79
00:06:06,960 --> 00:06:09,121
indicating lack of nourishment,
and unstable fetal signs.

80
00:06:09,121 --> 00:06:10,640
She requires complete rest.

81
00:06:15,041 --> 00:06:16,241
Don't worry too much.

82
00:06:16,601 --> 00:06:17,721
She should be fine.

83
00:06:24,400 --> 00:06:25,121
Mother.

84
00:06:25,760 --> 00:06:26,440
Mother.

85
00:06:27,280 --> 00:06:28,481
You've wronged the Empress.

86
00:06:28,721 --> 00:06:30,161
You've misunderstood her.

87
00:06:30,161 --> 00:06:32,640
Xu Yu harmed the imperial heir.

88
00:06:32,640 --> 00:06:34,400
How much longer will you shield her?

89
00:06:34,400 --> 00:06:35,041
Mother.

90
00:06:35,400 --> 00:06:36,801
Before you get the truth,

91
00:06:37,241 --> 00:06:38,320
aren't you being too hasty?

92
00:06:38,601 --> 00:06:40,921
If the imperial heir suffers any harm,

93
00:06:41,200 --> 00:06:43,440
I will not let the culprit
go unpunished.

94
00:06:44,520 --> 00:06:46,400
Now get back to your Fengyi Palace

95
00:06:47,561 --> 00:06:50,320
and pray for Lady Tao
and the unborn child.

96
00:06:50,760 --> 00:06:51,440
Mother!

97
00:06:57,760 --> 00:06:58,721
I take my leave.

98
00:06:59,161 --> 00:06:59,921
I'll go with you.

99
00:06:59,921 --> 00:07:00,880
Your Majesty.

100
00:07:01,481 --> 00:07:04,280
You should also spend some attention
on the other concubines.

101
00:07:04,601 --> 00:07:07,361
The child Lady Tao carries
is my imperial grandson.

102
00:07:10,280 --> 00:07:11,681
I will stay then.

103
00:07:27,361 --> 00:07:28,241
Eunuch Qin.

104
00:07:30,601 --> 00:07:32,121
Summon Xiao Jinming to the palace.

105
00:07:33,400 --> 00:07:34,681
My Empress,

106
00:07:34,681 --> 00:07:36,681
how can you spare the energy
to do it now?

107
00:07:36,681 --> 00:07:39,640
News of Lady Tao's unstable pregnancy
has spread everywhere.

108
00:07:39,640 --> 00:07:42,041
You'd better focus on
how to get yourself out of this.

109
00:07:42,280 --> 00:07:43,001
What?

110
00:07:44,041 --> 00:07:45,400
Do you also think it was my doing?

111
00:07:47,640 --> 00:07:50,960
(It feels like Xu Yu is walking
on thin ice in the imperial harem.)

112
00:07:51,121 --> 00:07:53,400
This matter definitely involves you.

113
00:07:56,001 --> 00:07:56,640
Jinming.

114
00:07:57,601 --> 00:07:58,280
You may leave.

115
00:07:58,280 --> 00:07:58,801
Yes.

116
00:08:01,921 --> 00:08:03,568
(Carefree)

117
00:08:10,200 --> 00:08:12,080
If you weren't as beautiful as a fairy,

118
00:08:12,080 --> 00:08:13,721
why would Jinyun
spend every night with you

119
00:08:13,721 --> 00:08:15,921
and provoke jealousy among the consorts?

120
00:08:15,921 --> 00:08:17,760
Otherwise, this heavy blame

121
00:08:17,960 --> 00:08:19,921
wouldn't have landed on you.

122
00:08:20,080 --> 00:08:22,840
Is that what you should say?

123
00:08:24,681 --> 00:08:25,721
Sister-in-law,

124
00:08:26,481 --> 00:08:27,921
why are you just like Jinyun?

125
00:08:34,560 --> 00:08:36,640
Can't you use your brain?

126
00:08:41,201 --> 00:08:43,880
Sister-in-law,
just poke me a few more times.

127
00:08:44,040 --> 00:08:44,601
Jinming.

128
00:08:45,760 --> 00:08:47,721
If you don't go handle something now,

129
00:08:48,040 --> 00:08:49,880
Jinyun will face imminent disaster.

130
00:08:54,560 --> 00:08:57,520
If this child had been born
to the Her Highness,

131
00:08:58,001 --> 00:08:59,040
Your Majesty,

132
00:08:59,441 --> 00:09:01,321
you would surely have been overjoyed.

133
00:09:06,160 --> 00:09:08,361
I know I can't compare
to the Her Highness.

134
00:09:08,680 --> 00:09:11,001
I only beg you
to spend more time with our child.

135
00:09:11,241 --> 00:09:12,280
That way,

136
00:09:12,760 --> 00:09:14,560
I will be fully content.

137
00:09:15,841 --> 00:09:18,201
Rest well and don't overthink.

138
00:09:23,241 --> 00:09:25,361
Did I accidentally press on your belly?

139
00:09:25,481 --> 00:09:26,920
No, Your Majesty.

140
00:09:27,441 --> 00:09:29,361
M-My belly...

141
00:09:30,560 --> 00:09:31,321
It hurts!

142
00:09:35,121 --> 00:09:35,841
Guards!

143
00:09:36,121 --> 00:09:37,472
Get the imperial physician!

144
00:09:41,280 --> 00:09:41,961
Your Majesty.

145
00:09:42,121 --> 00:09:43,241
I am incompetent.

146
00:09:43,601 --> 00:09:45,280
After the Empress collided with her,

147
00:09:45,560 --> 00:09:47,961
the imperial heir couldn't be saved.

148
00:09:50,481 --> 00:09:51,481
Your Majesty,

149
00:09:52,520 --> 00:09:54,640
I bear you no grudge.

150
00:09:55,841 --> 00:09:58,880
Why did you harm my child?

151
00:09:59,160 --> 00:09:59,841
Your Majesty.

152
00:10:00,160 --> 00:10:01,920
This concerns the imperial heir's life.

153
00:10:01,920 --> 00:10:04,280
How should we handle this?

154
00:10:04,800 --> 00:10:05,321
Mother.

155
00:10:05,841 --> 00:10:07,160
I'd like to ask you a question.

156
00:10:07,520 --> 00:10:10,400
Rumors say I caused Lady Tao's
miscarriage by bumping into her,

157
00:10:10,680 --> 00:10:12,321
thus destabilizing her pregnancy.

158
00:10:13,001 --> 00:10:15,520
Would I be foolish enough
to know the truth was exposed

159
00:10:15,520 --> 00:10:16,721
and still keep harming her?

160
00:10:17,040 --> 00:10:18,401
Isn't it like giving the evidence

161
00:10:18,401 --> 00:10:19,721
of my crime to others?

162
00:10:20,129 --> 00:10:20,680
Well...

163
00:10:22,121 --> 00:10:22,640
Mother.

164
00:10:22,880 --> 00:10:23,841
I believe the Empress.

165
00:10:24,400 --> 00:10:25,721
This matter is indeed suspicious.

166
00:10:26,241 --> 00:10:27,201
If it is suspicious,

167
00:10:27,601 --> 00:10:30,848
Jiang Tang, Head of imperial physicians,
can uncover the truth with examination.

168
00:10:31,201 --> 00:10:32,880
Jinyun, Mother.

169
00:10:33,481 --> 00:10:34,920
Jiang Tang came back from his leave.

170
00:10:35,081 --> 00:10:36,321
We've just examined the body.

171
00:10:37,321 --> 00:10:38,920
Your Majesty. Empress Dowager.

172
00:10:38,920 --> 00:10:39,920
(Jiang Tang,
Head of imperial physicians)

173
00:10:39,920 --> 00:10:42,601
The child Lady Tao carried
died days ago.

174
00:10:43,280 --> 00:10:44,400
What was delivered today

175
00:10:45,040 --> 00:10:46,201
was inevitably stillborn.

176
00:10:46,680 --> 00:10:48,841
Imperial Physician Feng
took Lady Tao's daily pulse,

177
00:10:49,680 --> 00:10:50,841
yet failed to detect it.

178
00:10:51,361 --> 00:10:52,241
You're lying!

179
00:10:52,721 --> 00:10:53,361
Impossible!

180
00:10:53,920 --> 00:10:54,640
Impossible!

181
00:10:54,880 --> 00:10:56,760
How could I harm my own child?

182
00:10:56,961 --> 00:10:57,721
Then tell me,

183
00:10:58,601 --> 00:10:59,481
did I push you?

184
00:11:00,121 --> 00:11:02,961
Or did you stage this to frame me?

185
00:11:03,280 --> 00:11:05,201
The truth is, your child died long ago.

186
00:11:09,361 --> 00:11:10,592
Imperial Physician Feng.

187
00:11:11,001 --> 00:11:12,481
Do you have anything to explain?

188
00:11:13,880 --> 00:11:14,721
Speak now!

189
00:11:15,321 --> 00:11:16,201
Please spare me!

190
00:11:16,201 --> 00:11:17,081
Have mercy!

191
00:11:17,081 --> 00:11:19,001
Lady Tao discovered the fetus had died,

192
00:11:19,001 --> 00:11:20,640
and tried to pin the blame
on the Empress.

193
00:11:20,640 --> 00:11:22,601
She forced me to do so.

194
00:11:31,001 --> 00:11:33,241
Lady Tao used the imperial heir
to frame the Empress,

195
00:11:33,241 --> 00:11:35,296
doubly guilty, is banished
to the cold palace.

196
00:11:35,560 --> 00:11:38,721
Imperial Physician Feng is imprisoned
to await trial.

197
00:12:01,520 --> 00:12:02,160
Master.

198
00:12:02,560 --> 00:12:04,920
Prince Xiaoyao has sent yarrow
from the Taihao Mausoleum.

199
00:12:05,800 --> 00:12:07,520
The turmoil in the palace has subsided.

200
00:12:07,520 --> 00:12:10,464
Prince Xiaoyao said he'll await
your comeback from seclusion tomorrow.

201
00:12:10,680 --> 00:12:12,040
The Purple Star moves retrograde.

202
00:12:12,520 --> 00:12:14,560
There's an omen
of the auspicious star and phoenix.

203
00:12:15,241 --> 00:12:16,841
How interesting!

204
00:12:23,041 --> 00:12:25,398
(Luo Hanying)

205
00:12:41,321 --> 00:12:42,800
You love your child deeply,

206
00:12:43,321 --> 00:12:45,001
but the person behind you

207
00:12:45,640 --> 00:12:47,520
only sees him as a bargaining chip

208
00:12:47,520 --> 00:12:48,640
and exploits him

209
00:12:49,001 --> 00:12:50,760
merely to achieve his own goals.

210
00:12:53,841 --> 00:12:55,481
I don't understand what you mean.

211
00:12:55,880 --> 00:12:58,601
It was my own plan
to use the child to drag you down.

212
00:12:58,601 --> 00:12:59,601
No one else is involved.

213
00:13:00,040 --> 00:13:00,800
Is it worth it?

214
00:13:01,201 --> 00:13:02,241
Yes.

215
00:13:02,880 --> 00:13:04,601
You were born the daughter of a marshal,

216
00:13:05,040 --> 00:13:06,944
and became the Empress
upon entering the palace.

217
00:13:07,601 --> 00:13:11,280
While I must exhaust myself
trying to please everyone.

218
00:13:11,961 --> 00:13:13,981
Usually, sincerity

219
00:13:14,273 --> 00:13:16,001
can only come with sincerity.

220
00:13:20,121 --> 00:13:21,121
Sincerity?

221
00:13:21,601 --> 00:13:23,441
If His Majesty sincerely loves you,

222
00:13:24,121 --> 00:13:25,880
how could he bear to let his Empress

223
00:13:25,880 --> 00:13:27,961
be trampled by a mere consort?

224
00:13:31,040 --> 00:13:32,040
Xu Yu.

225
00:13:33,280 --> 00:13:35,560
How much sincerity
do you have for His Majesty?

226
00:13:36,800 --> 00:13:39,441
Didn't you also marry him
for your family?

227
00:13:40,520 --> 00:13:41,880
People like us

228
00:13:42,481 --> 00:13:45,640
have never lived
a single day for ourselves.

229
00:13:47,160 --> 00:13:48,280
Sincerity?

230
00:13:49,201 --> 00:13:51,488
Sincerity is the least worthy thing
to be mentioned here.

231
00:14:02,160 --> 00:14:02,920
What's wrong?

232
00:14:04,001 --> 00:14:05,321
Don't cry! Don't cry!

233
00:14:05,520 --> 00:14:06,241
Mother is here.

234
00:14:06,520 --> 00:14:07,321
Mother is here.

235
00:14:08,001 --> 00:14:09,280
Don't cry!

236
00:14:22,201 --> 00:14:23,201
(Xu Yu.)

237
00:14:23,721 --> 00:14:25,880
(How much sincerity
do you have for His Majesty?)

238
00:14:26,361 --> 00:14:27,920
(Didn't you also marry him)

239
00:14:27,920 --> 00:14:29,040
(for your family?)

240
00:14:29,441 --> 00:14:31,776
(Sincerity is the least worthy thing
to be mentioned here.)

241
00:14:32,560 --> 00:14:33,920
(Lady Tao is wrong.)

242
00:14:34,241 --> 00:14:36,880
(If there's only one who's sincere
toward me within the harem,)

243
00:14:36,880 --> 00:14:38,201
(then it will only be Xu Yu.)

244
00:14:39,361 --> 00:14:40,040
Your Majesty.

245
00:14:44,680 --> 00:14:45,201
Your Majesty.

246
00:14:45,841 --> 00:14:46,760
What's wrong?

247
00:14:47,321 --> 00:14:49,560
Is something wrong with
the interrogation of Lady Tao?

248
00:14:51,721 --> 00:14:52,481
No.

249
00:14:53,760 --> 00:14:54,961
I just feel

250
00:14:56,001 --> 00:14:57,961
it's good that you are with me.

251
00:15:03,201 --> 00:15:03,841
Your Majesty.

252
00:15:09,601 --> 00:15:11,160
Has something happened to Lady Tao?

253
00:15:11,841 --> 00:15:14,160
You still care for her
despite her hatred toward you?

254
00:15:14,601 --> 00:15:16,321
It's true that Lady Tao framed me.

255
00:15:16,601 --> 00:15:18,560
But she genuinely cared for that child.

256
00:15:18,841 --> 00:15:20,201
That was her own child.

257
00:15:20,201 --> 00:15:21,560
How could she possibly harm him?

258
00:15:22,520 --> 00:15:23,400
Moreover,

259
00:15:24,880 --> 00:15:26,441
that is also your child.

260
00:15:28,001 --> 00:15:28,800
Xu Yu.

261
00:15:30,160 --> 00:15:32,400
My relationship with Lady Tao
isn't what you imagine.

262
00:15:32,920 --> 00:15:33,880
I never have...

263
00:15:33,880 --> 00:15:34,800
News!

264
00:15:37,800 --> 00:15:40,241
Your Majesties.
The Grand Preceptor has come back.

265
00:15:40,241 --> 00:15:41,880
Please go
to the Directorate of Astronomy.

266
00:16:01,825 --> 00:16:07,009
♪Parting clouds
to pluck the waxing moon♪

267
00:16:07,745 --> 00:16:12,308
♪Brewing a pot of bygone years♪

268
00:16:13,633 --> 00:16:19,048
♪Chill flame, window shade,
console my grieving soul♪

269
00:16:19,617 --> 00:16:24,161
♪Drunk through lifetimes
with no dreams returned♪

270
00:16:24,801 --> 00:16:30,065
♪If not for letting go, how could I
bear to shatter this dream♪

271
00:16:30,433 --> 00:16:36,110
♪Returning to drift
through the mortal world♪

272
00:16:36,449 --> 00:16:38,465
♪Like her, like me, like you♪

273
